20
00:04:00,083 --> 00:04:02,333
March Tenth, sunny.

21
00:04:02,416 --> 00:04:05,125
Up at 6 today,
first one up.

22
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,750
Authorities have identified
the woman who broke out

