00:04:11,833 --> 00:04:14,208
of the high-security and
purportedly escape-proof

24
00:04:14,291 --> 00:04:17,541
Diamandra Special Penitentiary
early yesterday morning.

25
00:04:17,625 --> 00:04:19,916
Her name is Michiko Malandro.

26
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,708
Under the cover of last night's
storm, she has disappeared,

27
00:04:22,791 --> 00:04:25,750
and as of yet, there have been
no reported sightings of her.

28
00:04:25,833 --> 00:04:28,416
Malandro should be considered
armed and extremely dangerous.

29
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:32,250
Which, as the outsider
