Apologize, right now!

198
00:15:48,416 --> 00:15:49,916
I told you to apologize!

199
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,041
For what?

200
00:15:51,125 --> 00:15:54,416
I didn't do,
I didn't do anything!

201
00:15:56,416 --> 00:15:59,125
