can challenge me now?

202
00:15:59,208 --> 00:16:00,458
Alright then!

203
00:16:02,166 --> 00:16:04,291
If that's the case, get out!

204
00:16:09,333 --> 00:16:11,000
We just don't need you here.

205
00:16:11,083 --> 00:16:13,416
And no one cares
about you anyway.

206
00:16:34,583 --> 00:16:35,916
I've had it!

207
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:38,583
I've put up with
this for too long!

208
00:16:38,666 --> 00:16:40,291
You treat me
like dirt every day,

209
00:16:40,375 --> 00:16:42,500
and you don't care
what that does to me!

210
00:16:42,583 --> 00:16:45,000
Do you even know I'm a person?

211
00:16:45,083 --> 00:16:47,750
Look at me!

212
00:16:47,833 --> 00:16:49,416
Look me right in the face!

213
00:16:49,500 --> 00:16:52,041
Good, now remember it!

214
00:17:04,916 --> 00:17:07,458
What the heck am I
supposed to do now?

215
00:17:07,541 --> 00:17:09,208
I can't go back.

216
00:17:12,583 --> 00:17:15,916
It was too scary to go
home alone, so I decided

217
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,208
to bring Branco back with me.

218
00:17:23,166 --> 00:17:27,458
Someone from down that road,
is going to come for me.

219
00:17:37,166 --> 00:17:39,500
Sorry about the wait, Hana.

220
00:17:41,833 --> 00:17:43,750
I came to get you.

221
00:17:47,666 --> 00:17:49,791
Yeah, that'll never happen.

222
00:17:54,208 --> 00:17:56,500
This the Belem-something
Yamada's?

223
00:17:56,583 --> 00:17:57,750
Yes.

224
00:17:57,833 --> 00:17:59,625
May I ask who's calling?

225
00:17:59,708 --> 00:18:01,541
Got a kid named Hana?

226
00:18:01,625 --> 00:18:04,000
I'll be there tomorrow,
get her ready.

227
00:18:04,083 --> 00:18:06,916
I'm sorry, but who
is this exactly?

228
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:08,333
Who am I?

229
00:18:09,875 --> 00:18:11,416
I'm her mother.

230
00:18:16,083 --> 00:18:19,541
Apparently, Hana's mother
is coming tomorrow.

231
00:18:19,625 --> 00:18:21,666
Her mother is dead,
isn't she?

232
00:18:21,750 --> 00:18:23,958
Well, that's what
I'd always heard.

233
00:18:24,041 --> 00:18:25,583
So what does this mean?

234
00:18:25,666 --> 00:18:27,333
Got me.

235
00:18:29,375 --> 00:18:31,458
Of course.

236
00:18:31,541 --> 00:18:33,250
Kidnapping.

237
00:18:34,958 --> 00:18:37,833
Clearly someone
jealous of my position.

238
00:18:37,916 --> 00:18:40,458
Yeah, must be.

239
00:18:40,541 --> 00:18:42,208
What are they after?

240
00:18:42,291 --> 00:18:43,583
Money?

241
00:18:43,666 --> 00:18:45,583
Or do they just wanna stick
it to me, by cutting off

242
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:49,333
our child support?

243
00:18:49,416 --> 00:18:52,416
Go and fetch my shotgun.

244
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:55,458
I'm gonna get these
sons of bitches first.

245
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:00,750
Amen.

246
00:19:00,833 --> 00:19:02,291
Dig in everyone.

247
00:19:20,875 --> 00:19:23,041
Go hide Hana somewhere safe.

248
00:20:03,250 --> 00:20:04,291
Hey!

249
00:20:06,708 --> 00:20:08,041
Yeah you, four-eyes.

250
00:20:08,125 --> 00:20:09,375
Look at me.

251
00:20:13,833 --> 00:20:15,833
Is your name Hana?

252
00:20:24,291 --> 00:20:26,041
Then it's you.

253
00:20:37,666 --> 00:20:43,083
She's just staring at me,
mouth hanging open.

254
00:20:43,166 --> 00:20:45,083
Not ladylike at all.

255
00:20:59,833 --> 00:21:01,291
C'mon, Hana.

256
00:21:01,375 --> 00:21:03,958
Or you gonna
sit there all day?

257
00:21:06,041 --> 00:21:08,208
"Someone is going
to come for me".

258
00:21:08,291 --> 00:21:12,208
It's what I'd wished for,
all this time.

259
00:21:12,291 --> 00:21:16,125
On the morning of March
Seventeenth, that person came.

260
00:21:19,083 --> 00:21:20,666
The only problem.

261
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:22,750
I have no idea who she is!

